  <h1>About Yoga &amp; Mindfulness Studio</h1>
  <p>We are a welcoming yoga and mindfulness studio offering a range of classes and workshops for people of all levels of fitness and ability. Whether you are a complete beginner or an experienced practitioner, our expert instructors will guide you on a journey to better health, flexibility, and inner peace.</p>

  <h2>What We Offer</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Weekly Block Courses</strong> &mdash; Structured multi-week programmes that build strength, flexibility, and mindfulness progressively. Perfect for developing a consistent practice.</li>
    <li><strong>Weekend Workshops</strong> &mdash; Intensive sessions held over a weekend, focusing on specific techniques such as breathwork, meditation, or advanced postures.</li>
    <li><strong>Drop-in Classes</strong> &mdash; Many of our weekly courses allow drop-in attendance, so you can join a single session without committing to a full block.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Class Levels</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Beginner</strong> &mdash; No experience needed. We start from the very basics of posture, breathing, and relaxation.</li>
    <li><strong>Intermediate</strong> &mdash; Some prior yoga or mindfulness experience is helpful. We build on fundamental techniques with more challenging sequences.</li>
    <li><strong>Advanced</strong> &mdash; For experienced practitioners ready for deeper practice, including advanced postures and extended meditation.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Our Studios</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Studio A</strong> &mdash; 12 High Street, Town Centre &ndash; Our main studio with underfloor heating and natural light.</li>
    <li><strong>Studio B</strong> &mdash; 4 Park Lane, East Quarter &ndash; A peaceful space surrounded by gardens, ideal for mindfulness sessions.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How to Book</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><a href="/auth/register">Create a free account</a> or <a href="/auth/login">log in</a>.</li>
    <li>Browse <a href="/courses">our courses</a> and find one that suits your level and schedule.</li>
    <li>Click &ldquo;View &amp; Book&rdquo; to enrol in a full course or book a drop-in session.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>Questions about our classes or need help choosing the right course? Get in touch at <a href="mailto:hello@yogamindfulness.example.com">hello@yogamindfulness.example.com</a> or call us on 0141 555 0123.</p>
